{"tid":1054314,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港01 我有料爆！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-03-09T17:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T22:55:11.000Z","uid":216008,"like":3501,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"934949e2f7aaac773be1719f591cfadda3d461fd","tid":1054314,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:36:36.000Z","msg":"首先啦 今朝我整左個飯比自己食 唔該你個標題打做《連登仔自己肯做飯》<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比埋圖你 廢事你左搵右搵咁辛苦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/khS81Q0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkhS81Q0.png&h=01afccda&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n之後呢 食完飯就同我partner執返劑 想改個煽情啲既名 《「基不是罪」同性戀的控訴》<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地基基錫下嘴仔都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZy4AbZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZy4AbZ.gif&h=cb69bde7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n夜晚就普通啲 食左個好撚難食既泰式飯 麻煩你幫我改呢個名《泰式不太識 網民：好X難食》<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKsAGSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKsAGSY.jpg&h=3d39f194&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n咁而家夜闌人靜 聽緊寂寞的男人 咁簡單啲 嚟個《網民很寂寞 聽寂寞的男人》<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29MqjGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29MqjGC.jpg&h=d5aed752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係咁你地就有四篇野喇</span></strong> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔該落返credit 連登仔/網民就得喇</strong></span><br />\n你地都只係拾人牙慧 何必等我地一兩日先一個你覺得正既post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係諗住抄野都要qc呀嘛</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d9934e42f7ea731397740cb576ab1c37bb5900","tid":1054314,"uid":216008,"like":756,"dislike":6,"score":750,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:42:00.000Z","msg":"我好想比01引用我啲料呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cb86f34dc1c7fba988f8adef23bce31bc51e8e","tid":1054314,"uid":78349,"like":294,"dislike":4,"score":290,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:51:41.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af13c14dc1fe83277c4829d9d42de46f607f0cb","tid":1054314,"uid":216008,"like":261,"dislike":3,"score":258,"quote":{"pid":"a0cb86f34dc1c7fba988f8adef23bce31bc51e8e","tid":1054314,"uid":78349,"like":294,"dislike":4,"score":290,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:51:41.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:53:13.000Z","msg":"多謝杜女士你一齊推post呀 十卜十卜！快啲比香港01見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79ed6db7f5f6b00befbc2522d6f845aa5f3f5ff","tid":1054314,"uid":3857,"like":291,"dislike":3,"score":288,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:58:46.000Z","msg":"各位記者我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed63f0b03a915517ee7f00910ff096947894890",